    *   **IEEE 802.11 Header Diagram**: A suggestion to include a figure of the 802.11 header, specifically regarding MAC address encryption, was discussed. Jerome expressed concern about maintaining accuracy due to evolving standards (e.g., 802.11bi encrypting MAC addresses) and suggested pointing to IEEE documents instead of duplicating content. A sense of those present indicated a preference against adding such detailed, evolving content directly into the document.
